{%- comment -%}
  Product Trust Badges Block
  
  A compact, vertical list of trust indicators designed to be placed
  within product details, typically below the "Add to Cart" button.
  
  Features:
  - Vertical layout (stacked badges)
  - Compact design for product pages
  - 3-4 recommended badges
  - Built-in icons
  - Customizable colors and spacing
  - No external dependencies
  
  Usage:
  Add this block within the Product Details section, ideally below
  the buy buttons to reduce purchase friction.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="product-trust-badges" style="
  --badge-gap: {{ block.settings.badge_gap }}px;
  --badge-text-color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  --badge-icon-color: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
